      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine. This unit maintains excellent compression across all cylinders and exhibits the immediate throttle response characteristic of its individual throttle bodies. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, sending power through a healthy M-Variable limited-slip differential. Crucial preventative maintenance has been performed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The suspension geometry remains true, offering the precise, communicative handling this chassis is renowned for. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain and cooling system are optimized for performance, making this an ideal candidate for the discerning driver.",
